# UGS HTML games — optional Git LFS. Recommended: store small HTML as normal git files (no LFS)
# so CI/App Hosting never see pointer stubs. If you keep LFS, Firebase Hosting build uses
# lfs:true and prebuild fails if pointers remain on disk.
#
# To drop LFS: remove the line below, run `git lfs pull`, then:
#   git rm --cached -r "Client/UGS Files" && git add "Client/UGS Files" && git commit
Client/UGS[[:space:]]Files/** filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
